SUMMARY:Yoga In Nature™ ALL LEVELS YOGA at For Garden's Sake
DESCRIPTION:Yoga In Nature™\, NC\n**So excited to be back and offer anot
 her Yoga In Nature™ event at For Garden's Sake!!!** ***\\*$25/person pai
 d at signup in advance to secure your spot***\\*.\\* \\*\\*\\*Pay by Venmo
  @Darlene-Genander (0862 if asked for 4 digits) or by PayPal dgenander@yog
 ainnature.com Message me for Zelle or Cash options.\n\nCome join us in the
  open field alongside the pond for a 60 minute vinyasa flow to yin practic
 e for **ALL LEVELS and first timers.** We will gather as a community in a 
 yoga practice that will focus on flowing with our breath as we move our bo
 dies and connect with nature\, being guided with all o four senses. No exp
 erience necessary\, just an open mind:) We will plant seeds for our growth
  on and off our mats. You will also receive a small gift at this event!\n\
 nBring a friend! Gift someone special who loves yoga and/or plants. Stay f
 or hot tea following the practice. Wander the grounds of the garden center
 's indoor and outdoor plants\, shrubs and trees for your own home or inspi
 ration. Also\, take a look at their potting shed and visit with the goats 
 and ducks on the property.\n\nBring your own yoga mat and/or towel\, water
  bottle\, and whatever you may need for your practice. Sunscreen\, if need
 ed\, as we will be in open field under the sun.\n\nTentative rain date wil
 l be April 19\, if needed. If there is a rain date\, and you are unable to
  make it\, you will be reimbursed.
