SUMMARY:YOGA IN NATURE™: ALL LEVELS Lake Johnson
DESCRIPTION:Yoga In Nature™\, NC\n**EARTH DAY YOGA SLOW FLOW and celebra
 ting YOGA IN NATURE™ 7 years!!!**\nPLEASE ARRIVE EARLY TO GET PARKING AN
 D FOR 5-10 MINUTE WALK TO THE LOCATION. Along Lake Johnson\, Raleigh. in o
 pen meadow\, above the lake. This was such a delightful discovery!!! I wil
 l be sending out exact location\, as there isn't a pin on the map for this
  one for practice. If you haven't been to a class with me here\, please me
 ssage me.\n\nALL LEVELS YOGA\, INCLUDING NEW AND BEGINNERS. Come join our 
 community as we explore our yoga and nature. 60 minute beginner to interme
 diate yoga class (options for all levels taught) beginning with a slower v
 inyasa flow to yin practice\, ending in savasana.\n\nBring a mat\, towel o
 r liner for under your mat to protect it (if ground is damp or wet)\, suns
 creen\, insect repellant\, water\, block or anything you may need for your
  outdoor practice. There will be shade and sun options for your practice.\
 n\nYou may want to pack walking shoes\, a book\, snack\, journal to make i
 t a longer commune with nature.
